results.name: Sum of distinct prime divisors of n that are < sqrt(n).
mathematica: nmax = 90; CoefficientList[Series[Sum[Prime[k] x^(Prime[k] (Prime[k] + 1))/(1 - x^Prime[k]), {k, 1, nmax}], {x, 0, nmax}], x] // Rest
